WEBVTT

00:00:19.874 --> 00:00:25.048
I’m sitting here this afternoon with Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:00:25.129 --> 00:00:26.822
Is that how I say your name, Shri Mataji?

00:00:26.902 --> 00:00:29.000
That’s correct, it’s correct.

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:32.280
Shri Mataji is a world-renowned spiritual leader,

00:00:32.360 --> 00:00:34.760
and we’re very happy to welcome you here today.

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:36.559
Thank you very much.

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:40.920
Shri Mataji. Can you tell us when you first realized

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.280
that you had this special spiritual gift?

00:00:47.853 --> 00:00:53.359
You see, it’s like this, that when we are bornp
as human beings, we know we are human beings.

00:00:53.440 --> 00:01:00.096
In the same way, I knew from my very birth that I was something of that kind.

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:05.872
And since you’ve been a young person, you’ve been spreading

00:01:05.953 --> 00:01:12.839
this spiritual message, or is this something that you’ve just recently begun to do?

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:17.759
No, I had to wait and see certain things about human beings.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:24.059
Because I had to study why human beings cannot get Realization en masse.

00:01:24.139 --> 00:01:26.240
They should get it en masse, otherwise,

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:29.120
if one person gets it, then people don’t understand them.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:33.039
They crucify them, they poison them, they’ve tortured them.

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:37.720
So why shouldn’t it work out en masse? And so, I had to study

00:01:37.801 --> 00:01:41.519
for years together. At the age of my 47th year,

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:49.719
I discovered a method by which Self-realization can be achieved en masse.

00:01:49.800 --> 00:01:52.920
Shri Mataji, you use the term Self-realization.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:56.480
That’s a term we’re not really very familiar with here in America.

00:01:56.560 --> 00:01:59.080
Can you explain that to me?

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:03.999
It’s the same as what Christ has said that, “You are to be born again”.

00:02:04.119 --> 00:02:08.719
That is when, like a bird, you see, you are an egg,

00:02:08.800 --> 00:02:11.336
and then you become a bird.

00:02:11.416 --> 00:02:15.912
And also a bird is called a ‘twice-born’ in Sanskrit language.

00:02:15.992 --> 00:02:22.199
In the same way, a human being is bound by his conditioning, by his ego,

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:30.504
but when he is born again, then he is called as a
Self-realized person,

00:02:30.584 --> 00:02:34.571
because he knows about himself, about his inner being.

00:02:34.651 --> 00:02:40.799
And also he’s endowed on his central nervous system with a new awareness

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:46.039
that Jung had described as Collective Consciousness.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:50.799
So it’s not just a certificate one can give that you are baptized,

00:02:50.880 --> 00:02:55.359
or you are Self-realized, or you are twice-born.

00:02:55.440 --> 00:03:00.280
It’s a living process, which is the last breakthrough

00:03:00.361 --> 00:03:04.521
in your awareness, where you become.

00:03:04.601 --> 00:03:06.114
It’s a question of becoming.

00:03:06.194 --> 00:03:12.746
You become a personality which can feel the All-pervading Power,

00:03:12.826 --> 00:03:19.559
about which every scripture has described, on your central nervous system.

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:23.799
This is what we call as ‘bodh’, as in Buddha,

00:03:23.880 --> 00:03:28.280
called as ‘Veda’, as in Veda. Means you have to know it

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:32.560
on your central nervous system, on your fingertips,

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:37.200
as Mohammed Sahib has said that, “You have to know it on your fingertips”

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:45.519
that it exists all around you, like a very beautiful, soothing, cool breeze.

00:03:45.600 --> 00:03:48.600
This is the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:51.680
So Shri Mataji, what you are describing then,

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:56.040
is a process that comes from inside each of us,

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:59.879
and is something that everyone can feel,
or just a few people?

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:05.256
No, everybody can feel. ‘Sahaja’, you see, we call it a Sahaja Yoga.

00:04:05.350 --> 00:04:08.119
Sahaja means born with you.

00:04:08.200 --> 00:04:13.390
It is born with you, this yoga,

00:04:13.470 --> 00:04:16.821
or we can say this promise of yoga is born with you.

00:04:16.901 --> 00:04:19.559
It means there is a power within you,

00:04:19.640 --> 00:04:23.039
which is called in Sanskrit language as Kundalini,

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:28.159
which resides in the triangular bone, which, surprisingly,

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:32.800
the Greeks called as sacrum bone.
That means they knew it’s a sacred bone.

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:37.110
And this is the fourth power which resides within us,

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:44.120
and which somehow or other awakened, pierces through your fontanel bone area,

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:52.280
and you really get the experience of actualization of your second birth,

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:57.320
by feeling the cool breeze coming out of your head, you yourself.

00:04:57.400 --> 00:05:00.560
And you can experience it on your fingertips.

00:05:00.640 --> 00:05:05.455
It’s not just imagination. You have to certify yourself.

00:05:06.079 --> 00:05:09.639
Well Shri Mataji, It sounds extremely simple.

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:13.840
How does one have this feeling coming from their fingertips,

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:16.880
and a cool breeze coming from the top of the head?

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:24.360
Everything vital has to be simple. See how a seed sprouts.

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:26.559
They have to just put it in the Mother Earth.

00:05:26.640 --> 00:05:30.159
The Mother Earth has got the capacity to sprout it,

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:34.400
and the seed has all the built-in machinery in it.

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:37.360
In the same way, you too have everything within you,

00:05:37.440 --> 00:05:39.479
and it just sprouts.

00:05:39.560 --> 00:05:44.280
So Shri Mataji, once this is sprouted, then what?

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:48.040
What happens to me? Do I become different?

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:53.960
You start transforming completely, because you get the light.

00:05:54.080 --> 00:05:58.980
When there is no light, you can catch hold of a snake
thinking it’s a rope.

00:05:59.060 --> 00:06:05.480
But when there’s light, you can see it yourself
and you drop it. So you can see the saints,

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:08.440
who are real saints, incarnations, prophets,

00:06:08.520 --> 00:06:12.080
they never committed mistakes. We might think they committed mistakes

00:06:12.160 --> 00:06:15.280
because our knowledge about them is limited.

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:18.600
But they never committed mistakes, they never committed sins,

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:22.960
because they were connected with the Divine Power,

00:06:23.040 --> 00:06:26.102
because they were Self-realized.

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:29.200
Well, the transforming power that you describe, then,

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:33.800
is something that once it happens to me, I keep it for myself.

00:06:33.880 --> 00:06:38.520
Can I give this transformation power to my friends or my relatives?

00:06:38.600 --> 00:06:39.920
Or is it just mine?

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:43.520
No, no, of course. A light which is lightened

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:46.440
is not kept under the table, as Christ has told.

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:48.640
In the same way, when you are enlightened,

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:52.160
you can enlighten other people. You are endowed with that power.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:55.513
You have those powers, then you can do it.

00:06:55.959 --> 00:07:00.999
Because it passes through your seven subtle, six subtle centres,

00:07:01.080 --> 00:07:08.959
and pierces through your last center of limbic area, which is nourished,

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:12.507
which is being made knowledgeable.

00:07:12.587 --> 00:07:17.240
So when you start giving this to others,

00:07:17.320 --> 00:07:21.640
you can feel the centres of other people on your fingertips,

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:26.200
and you know what is their problem. Only thing, if you have to know,

00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:32.360
only if you can know, how to get rid of those obstacles

00:07:32.440 --> 00:07:36.504
of these subtle centres, you can manage it.

00:07:36.714 --> 00:07:42.052
So what you’re saying is once this power is awakened in each of us,

00:07:42.132 --> 00:07:47.560
then the normal problems of humanity, the problems of health

00:07:47.640 --> 00:07:54.200
or stress or of nervousness will go away?

00:07:54.280 --> 00:07:55.973
That’s the minimum.

00:07:56.053 --> 00:07:57.860
There is more?

00:07:57.940 --> 00:08:03.598
That’s the minimum that would happen. It cures so many incurable diseases.

00:08:04.931 --> 00:08:09.706
And it also gives you better peace.

00:08:09.786 --> 00:08:14.363
It has cured many mental cases.

00:08:14.443 --> 00:08:19.979
People have got rid of many drug habits, alcoholism,

00:08:20.059 --> 00:08:25.295
because, as I told you, you see the snake and you drop it.

00:08:25.375 --> 00:08:30.319
Also you become very powerful but not aggressive, very compassionate.

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:32.880
I think that’s what Americans would worry,

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:37.200
whether they would just become a nation of very passive people.

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:40.440
That is not the case then with this meditation technique?

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:43.160
Not at all. You become very dynamic.

00:08:43.280 --> 00:08:48.160
You see, actually, you are passive when you are afraid of something,

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:51.560
when you don’t know anything. Then you become passive.

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:55.040
But you become dynamic when you know everything,

00:08:55.160 --> 00:08:57.960
and you know you are not doing anything wrong,

00:08:58.040 --> 00:09:00.670
so you are not afraid of anything.

00:09:01.159 --> 00:09:05.479
Shri Mataji, in the background information we received,

00:09:05.560 --> 00:09:11.440
I know you’ve travelled around the world for several years, 19 or 20,

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:15.280
and you’ve been spreading this message. When you came to America,

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:19.480
I believe it was in the early 1970s. You came at that time

00:09:19.560 --> 00:09:23.720
with not only this message, but a message about false gurus.

00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:27.120
And in the 1980s, you warned us again

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:33.280
that we needed the Self-realization, and that AIDS was on the horizon.

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:36.960
Is there a message that you have for us for the 1990s?

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:40.840
What’s the use? Even if I tell you, people won’t listen.

00:09:40.960 --> 00:09:44.240
I’ve told them about AIDS. I’ve told them about a kind

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:49.200
of a paralysis of the conscious mind. That’s working out already.

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:55.920
Also about very speedy people, very speedy children,

00:09:56.039 --> 00:09:57.840
but they don’t listen.

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:02.937
The trouble of Americans is this, that they think everything is money.

00:10:03.017 --> 00:10:05.400
And those who make them pay,

00:10:05.480 --> 00:10:10.799
or those whom they can purchase with money, they listen to them.

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:14.308
If Christ was here, they would not have listened to Him either,

00:10:14.388 --> 00:10:17.969
because you cannot purchase Christ, you cannot purchase Me.

00:10:18.049 --> 00:10:20.280
So those who can make money,

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:26.680
those who can make business out of all this, then they will listen.

00:10:26.760 --> 00:10:35.119
And those who really know the job, those who really know the Divine Power,

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:40.280
those who are honest, will never take any money for this,

00:10:40.360 --> 00:10:42.910
because you cannot pay for it.

00:10:43.240 --> 00:10:46.160
Well, that brings me to the New Age, Shri Mataji.

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:51.791
Here in America, we’re very involved in the so-called New Age
of Enlightenment.

00:10:51.871 --> 00:10:57.040
We invest in crystals, we invest in channelling sessions,

00:10:57.121 --> 00:11:01.040
we have exotic diets, we jog.

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:07.240
How does Sahaja Yoga differ from the other New Age phenomena
that we’re seeing?

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:12.560
It’s all artificial things. Artificiality is not going to give you

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:17.392
that personality which comes through inner transformation.

00:11:17.473 --> 00:11:20.600
And that’s why this yoga, this union with the Divine,

00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:24.760
has to be established. Now supposing if a tree is sick,

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:27.920
and we try to put some ointment on its leaves,

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:31.800
do you think the tree will be cured? We have to go to the roots.

00:11:31.880 --> 00:11:34.560
In the same way, we have to go to the roots.

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:38.840
And Sahaja Yoga deals with your roots, not with your outside.

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:41.560
I see. You mentioned money, Shri Mataji.

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:45.913
And of course, many people are getting rich
with the New Age seminars,

00:11:45.993 --> 00:11:50.783
and New Age books and crystals, and other paraphernalia.

00:11:50.863 --> 00:11:53.520
Sahaja Yoga does cost money, doesn’t it?

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:55.996
No, it does not at all. You cannot pay for it.

00:11:56.077 --> 00:11:58.680
It does not cost you money. Of course, I mean, supposing

00:11:58.760 --> 00:12:03.255
you have to come and see me here, you have to pay for the taxi, that’s all.

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:06.892
I’m not supposed to pay for that.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:13.000
And that’s all? That’s the only cost, just whatever cost you incur

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:15.562
in getting the message?

00:12:15.643 --> 00:12:20.200
Of course. Because this is a living process.

00:12:20.320 --> 00:12:24.178
And anything living does not understand money.

00:12:24.259 --> 00:12:27.595
I see. Shri Mataji, here in America,

00:12:27.675 --> 00:12:33.276
we have what many people view as two separate societies.

00:12:33.356 --> 00:12:42.611
We have a society on the one hand that is very
affluent, very wealthy, technological advancements.

00:12:42.692 --> 00:12:49.120
And then on the other hand, we have an America that is impoverished
morally, socially.

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:53.271
We have crimes and child abuse.

00:12:53.351 --> 00:12:59.246
What is the explanation for these two separate Americas existing at the same time?

00:12:59.326 --> 00:13:05.799
And how can we get rid of those negative aspects that are becoming so prominent
in American life?

00:13:05.880 --> 00:13:10.240
There’s imbalance in life. They are completely imbalanced people,

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:14.200
because they run after money. Hook or crook, get money.

00:13:14.280 --> 00:13:17.680
Do what you like. Women think that even selling

00:13:17.760 --> 00:13:20.680
their chastity is all right because you get money.

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:26.201
“What’s wrong?” They can sell everything. So there’s no sense of morality

00:13:26.282 --> 00:13:28.680
within them. And that’s why all these things start.

00:13:28.760 --> 00:13:32.400
For example, drugs do not come from the people who are addicted to drugs,

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:36.280
but the ones who sell drugs.
They sell drugs because they get money.

00:13:36.360 --> 00:13:40.360
They are not bothered as to how many people they are ruining by that.

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:42.840
So, it’s a money orientation in everything.

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:49.505
It’s an extreme behaviour towards money.

00:13:49.585 --> 00:13:55.560
Money has its own place and it should be treated in its own limitations and understanding.

00:13:55.680 --> 00:14:01.520
So when you go headlong with this idea of getting money,

00:14:01.600 --> 00:14:07.800
you enter into all these blind alleys where you get lost.

00:14:07.920 --> 00:14:10.200
Well, are you a socialist Shri Mataji?

00:14:10.280 --> 00:14:14.679
I’m not a socialist, nor am I a capitalist, but I’m both.

00:14:14.760 --> 00:14:18.080
Because I have all the capital, because I have the powers,

00:14:18.200 --> 00:14:23.528
and I’m a socialist because I can’t live without distributing it.

00:14:23.960 --> 00:14:27.642
And that’s what you do on a daily basis.

00:14:28.255 --> 00:14:30.320
When we talk about transformation,

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:34.080
Shri Mataji, many of us look at our planet Earth

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:40.385
and see the ecological changes, the disasters, all over the world.

00:14:40.466 --> 00:14:43.239
Here in America, one moment we have drought

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:48.600
and the next moment we have flooding. Is that also part of this imbalance?

00:14:48.680 --> 00:14:54.760
Absolutely. Absolutely. You see, we have to know that machinery

00:14:54.840 --> 00:14:58.719
or technology is for us. We are not for them.

00:14:58.800 --> 00:15:02.880
There has to be a balance of how far to go with machinery

00:15:03.000 --> 00:15:05.750
and how far to go with technology also.

00:15:05.830 --> 00:15:10.759
One day may be that this technology will become a big devil and start killing us.

00:15:10.846 --> 00:15:13.685
Where have we reached with science also?

00:15:13.770 --> 00:15:18.652
We have got hydrogen bomb, atomic bomb,

00:15:18.760 --> 00:15:22.840
then we are creating acid rain, all kinds of problems.

00:15:22.920 --> 00:15:29.320
So the technology has no balance. While the knowledge of the Spirit

00:15:29.440 --> 00:15:36.920
is not one-sided, mental enterprises are only linear

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:40.040
and they recoil on you.

00:15:40.120 --> 00:15:44.138
But the spiritual enterprise is on all sides.

00:15:44.218 --> 00:15:48.943
So it keeps complete balance and integration.

00:15:49.520 --> 00:15:56.960
So, what then, if I’m understanding, is if we become spiritually enlightened,

00:15:57.040 --> 00:16:01.440
Self-realized as you call it, even our planet will change

00:16:01.520 --> 00:16:05.080
and the disasters that we see would lessen?

00:16:05.160 --> 00:16:08.360
Of course. All problems are created by human beings only.

00:16:08.440 --> 00:16:12.616
The planet has created no problem.

00:16:12.696 --> 00:16:16.640
So, if the human beings change, it will.

00:16:16.720 --> 00:16:20.720
And I think we don’t need so many to change.

00:16:20.840 --> 00:16:29.562
Only some good people to change, so they can influence others.

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:34.266
What we need are leaders, good leaders.

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:39.660
We’ve had some good leaders here in America, Shri Mataji,

00:16:39.880 --> 00:16:43.640
certainly I think I’ve heard you mention Abraham Lincoln.

00:16:43.721 --> 00:16:44.332
Of course.

00:16:44.413 --> 00:16:46.880
What were the qualities that Abraham Lincoln had

00:16:46.960 --> 00:16:50.280
that we in America should try and emulate more?

00:16:50.360 --> 00:16:54.677
He was an enlightened soul, absolutely an enlightened soul in every way.

00:16:54.757 --> 00:17:00.357
And how he lived collectively, he thought of collective.

00:17:00.437 --> 00:17:08.280
The way he looked after all the sides of life, that’s the sign of a Realized soul.

00:17:08.400 --> 00:17:13.469
But I don’t think now in America they value him so much as they should have.

00:17:13.549 --> 00:17:17.880
But one day, when they’ll be spiritually endowed, they’ll value him very much.

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:22.840
I saw a small little road somewhere in New York in his name

00:17:22.920 --> 00:17:24.674
and I was surprised.

00:17:25.886 --> 00:17:29.440
Some school buildings also have his name, Shri Mataji.

00:17:29.520 --> 00:17:33.532
Oh, I mean, you have to take a microscope to see that.

00:17:33.613 --> 00:17:36.960
Shri Mataji, I think that’s one of the problems here in America.

00:17:37.040 --> 00:17:43.080
We seem not to have the kinds of heroes that we need to have,

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:50.720
to give the role models. But just getting away from America,

00:17:50.800 --> 00:17:59.099
and just looking on a global scope, we see transformations in several countries.

00:17:59.179 --> 00:18:02.600
China and India have reestablished ties.

00:18:02.680 --> 00:18:06.886
Soviet Union and America have reestablished ties.

00:18:07.840 --> 00:18:12.440
Is there something going on globally that is causing nations

00:18:12.520 --> 00:18:18.910
that we perceive to be imbalanced to suddenly transform and become balanced?

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:22.120
You see, now the communication has improved

00:18:22.240 --> 00:18:26.920
and people see each other now and everybody thinks others are better.

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:30.600
Like Russians think Americans are in the heavens

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:34.200
and the Americans think that the Russians are in the heavens.

00:18:34.320 --> 00:18:37.827
It’s not understanding.

00:18:37.907 --> 00:18:43.320
When they are transforming, they should also see into what ditch they are.

00:18:43.440 --> 00:18:46.200
They should find out what problems there are.

00:18:46.320 --> 00:18:48.840
And when they are trying to transform themselves,

00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:53.720
they should see that they don’t, not fall into those ditches.

00:18:53.840 --> 00:18:58.400
Then only it will work out. Otherwise, just copying somebody else

00:18:58.480 --> 00:19:02.680
or following somebody else, it’s very artificial transformation

00:19:02.800 --> 00:19:05.440
and they will be in the same lurch.

00:19:05.560 --> 00:19:08.200
Well, that brings me to the China’s situation,

00:19:08.280 --> 00:19:13.640
certainly there’s been massive demonstrations for the past few weeks,

00:19:13.760 --> 00:19:18.560
where they’re looking to reform to become more democratic.

00:19:18.680 --> 00:19:22.800
Is your implication that just adopting our form of democracy

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:25.240
is not China’s answer?

00:19:25.360 --> 00:19:29.120
Not at all. There will be another ‘demonocracy’.

00:19:29.240 --> 00:19:32.957
Not at all. I don’t think this kind of a democracy is of any use,

00:19:33.037 --> 00:19:35.640
where there’s no sense of authority,

00:19:35.720 --> 00:19:40.997
there’s no sense of shame, there’s no sense of

00:19:41.078 --> 00:19:46.075
collective understanding. This kind of a democracy

00:19:46.156 --> 00:19:51.396
is not going to work out. And Chinese think that you people

00:19:51.600 --> 00:19:54.400
have lots of money, you have big, big cars

00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:58.476
and you have other things of which you are fed up now.

00:19:58.613 --> 00:20:03.899
Otherwise, why should you take to drugs? But they don’t see the other side of it.

00:20:04.440 --> 00:20:08.600
But I don’t say that what Chinese are, they are all right.

00:20:08.720 --> 00:20:12.143
They all have to become ‘Sahaj’ to enjoy.

00:20:12.223 --> 00:20:16.123
Then the whole political scene will change.

00:20:16.203 --> 00:20:21.619
People will just think about the benevolence and a balanced living.

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:27.640
You’ve established Sahaj in 30 countries, Shri Mataji.

00:20:30.086 --> 00:20:36.359
Tell me, besides India, where all of us here in America realize

00:20:36.440 --> 00:20:40.200
the spiritual life is of vast importance,

00:20:40.280 --> 00:20:44.160
is there another country that comes close to the spiritual side

00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:46.247
that India portrays?

00:20:50.040 --> 00:20:53.960
I would say Turkey is very close to India.

00:20:54.040 --> 00:21:00.880
So if you exclude Turkey, then you can say Italy. Italy.

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:06.960
Italian government, Italian people, they’re very spiritually alert.

00:21:07.080 --> 00:21:09.930
They understand the spiritual person.

00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:15.720
And Americans, for example, are not as sensitive?

00:21:15.840 --> 00:21:22.280
They are more sensitive to guru shopping. If there’s somebody selling,

00:21:22.360 --> 00:21:25.520
then they are happy. Here, if you are not selling,

00:21:25.600 --> 00:21:30.486
they are not happy. You have to have Rolls Royce’s to impress them.

00:21:30.566 --> 00:21:37.465
So with such kind of attitude, I don’t know how far I can go with them.

00:21:37.559 --> 00:21:43.519
Well, Shri Mataji, you’re obviously very persistent

00:21:43.680 --> 00:21:47.520
because you’ve worked at this for at least 20 years.

00:21:47.600 --> 00:21:53.040
Is there something that Americans can do to become a bit more sensitive?

00:21:53.120 --> 00:21:58.520
I understand there’s a money orientation. But is there something that we can do

00:21:58.600 --> 00:22:04.907
on a day-to-day life to begin to understand the spiritual need?

00:22:05.100 --> 00:22:08.400
They have to see the shock waiting for them.

00:22:08.520 --> 00:22:14.520
They have to see what problems there are, and not to evade and glorify them.

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:20.440
Whatever problems they have, they make a big, big drama out of it,

00:22:20.520 --> 00:22:24.280
and think that something, “This is very great”.

00:22:24.400 --> 00:22:28.520
So they should understand that this was a mistake, this was wrong.

00:22:28.640 --> 00:22:33.440
Accept your mistakes and then understand that this is not for your benevolence

00:22:33.520 --> 00:22:38.320
at all! It is for your destruction. These are all destructive powers

00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:42.880
which are working within you, because these are transitory things.

00:22:43.000 --> 00:22:46.400
And things which are transitory are transitory

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:49.520
because they have a built-in power to get destroyed.

00:22:49.600 --> 00:22:55.706
Otherwise, why are they transitory? So you have to seek the eternal.

00:22:56.560 --> 00:22:59.360
Shri Mataji, as you travel through America,

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:04.760
is there any state that’s more receptive to your message than any other?

00:23:04.880 --> 00:23:08.936
Is there anywhere in America that’s sensitive?

00:23:12.246 --> 00:23:15.439
I think San Diego is a good place, San Diego.

00:23:15.520 --> 00:23:19.560
I went there before also. First time I visited San Diego,

00:23:19.640 --> 00:23:25.880
there was a parapsychology institution. And I told them that,

00:23:25.960 --> 00:23:28.840
“This is all very wrong, it’s all negative forces.

00:23:28.920 --> 00:23:34.157
Don’t indulge into these things, this is all black magic, this is not good”.

00:23:34.237 --> 00:23:38.130
And they were very angry, of course. I mean, it was not very good of Me also,

00:23:38.210 --> 00:23:41.618
because I was supposed to be their guest, and I shouldn’t tell them off.

00:23:41.698 --> 00:23:45.920
But I didn’t know what parapsychology means. Parapsychology actually,

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:50.160
according to Sanskrit style, ‘para’ will be the ‘above’ psychology.

00:23:50.240 --> 00:23:54.600
But it was even below psychology. So, I thought I should not mislead them

00:23:54.680 --> 00:23:57.440
and I must tell them frankly, because I am a Mother

00:23:57.520 --> 00:24:01.200
and I shouldn’t tell them lies. But now we find

00:24:01.280 --> 00:24:05.160
it’s all destroyed already. People who were running it are destroyed.

00:24:05.280 --> 00:24:07.960
And those who were there, they came back to Me

00:24:08.040 --> 00:24:12.400
and that’s why in, San Diego, we have a better center.

00:24:12.520 --> 00:24:16.280
Maybe the sea is helping them, I don’t know what is helping them.

00:24:16.360 --> 00:24:21.840
But San Diego is the best place, I think, where today we find Sahaja Yogis

00:24:21.920 --> 00:24:23.751
developing better.

00:24:24.760 --> 00:24:29.240
Shri Mataji, You’ve travelled certainly extensively

00:24:29.320 --> 00:24:33.880
and I should mention that You’ve been married 45 years

00:24:33.960 --> 00:24:38.400
to a very prominent figure, Mr. C.P. Srivastava,

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:42.880
of the United Nations. And I wonder, in your travels,

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:47.720
I mean, we in America have such difficulty juggling jobs and families

00:24:47.800 --> 00:24:52.120
and extracurricular activities. How have you managed

00:24:52.200 --> 00:24:54.486
to have your marriage survive?

00:24:54.606 --> 00:25:00.280
Oh, we are very happily married. You see, actually, I was a housewife,

00:25:00.360 --> 00:25:04.200
so I waited till my daughters got married. And it all timed with it,

00:25:04.280 --> 00:25:07.440
that I discovered also this en masse method,

00:25:07.520 --> 00:25:12.200
after my daughters were married. I have two daughters.

00:25:12.320 --> 00:25:19.280
Then my husband also got elected to this job by 134 nations.

00:25:19.360 --> 00:25:23.160
So, fortunately and unfortunately he has to also travel a lot.

00:25:24.360 --> 00:25:29.440
And I have always given him all freedom that he needed to travel,

00:25:29.520 --> 00:25:33.720
even before he came to London on this job.

00:25:35.120 --> 00:25:40.240
So he realizes that it’s very important work I am doing.

00:25:40.320 --> 00:25:46.640
He himself has said that, “To transform one person is difficult.

00:25:46.720 --> 00:25:51.280
You have transformed so many people”. He always used to say that,

00:25:51.360 --> 00:25:55.120
“You are something great, but you can’t make others like you”.

00:25:55.200 --> 00:26:00.920
But now he says, “My honesty compels me to admit

00:26:01.000 --> 00:26:05.400
that this is a tremendous work and this will really create

00:26:06.800 --> 00:26:10.600
real united nations. Because it will come from within”.

00:26:12.120 --> 00:26:15.280
So he’s been working with the United Nations

00:26:15.360 --> 00:26:17.944
and sees your work as valuable if not more.

00:26:18.024 --> 00:26:23.759
Yes, he’s the senior most Secretary General now.
He’s the senior most Secretary General, my husband.

00:26:23.840 --> 00:26:26.280
And yet he finds your work to be of great value.

00:26:26.360 --> 00:26:29.049
Of very great importance.

00:26:29.130 --> 00:26:32.120
Well, Shri Mataji, obviously, in your vision,

00:26:32.200 --> 00:26:36.040
you see personal transformation, people becoming healthy,

00:26:36.120 --> 00:26:39.720
people becoming well. Nations growing

00:26:39.800 --> 00:26:44.080
and embracing other nations. What’s the role of America

00:26:44.160 --> 00:26:46.440
in this global transformation?

00:26:46.520 --> 00:26:50.999
Very great. America doesn’t know what

00:26:51.080 --> 00:26:56.960
is the role of America is. America is the one which stands

00:26:57.040 --> 00:27:01.680
for collectivity. It has to spread collectivity

00:27:01.760 --> 00:27:05.240
and communications. It has the power of communications.

00:27:05.320 --> 00:27:07.480
All these technology and all those things,

00:27:07.560 --> 00:27:15.120
have come to America for communication. And communication is going to work out.

00:27:16.240 --> 00:27:18.960
So, all those false gurus who have come to America

00:27:19.040 --> 00:27:23.800
suddenly become overnight, well-known people in the whole world,

00:27:23.920 --> 00:27:30.520
because they have a big name in America. Or the communication that we have

00:27:31.840 --> 00:27:37.720
through our talks, through our messages, through our lectures,

00:27:37.800 --> 00:27:42.120
all these are very important. And they have to guard themselves

00:27:42.200 --> 00:27:51.360
as to what they are talking about. Also, they are very busy helping nations

00:27:51.480 --> 00:27:59.480
here and there, like Vietnam and Korea, Nicaragua, all sorts of things.

00:28:01.040 --> 00:28:04.200
But the discrimination part, which is very important

00:28:04.280 --> 00:28:08.120
for communication, is slightly likely.

00:28:08.240 --> 00:28:15.080
If they knew how to discriminate, they would be of the greatest help

00:28:15.160 --> 00:28:19.720
for the Divine work. But this discrimination can only come

00:28:19.800 --> 00:28:22.080
after they have this transformation.

00:28:24.360 --> 00:28:29.280
Well, you spoke of a few good people in America getting this transformation

00:28:29.360 --> 00:28:36.080
and then this discrimination. Do you have hopes that this will

00:28:36.160 --> 00:28:38.680
take place in the next decade?

00:28:38.760 --> 00:28:43.240
It has to, I’m very hopeful. America has to realize.

00:28:43.320 --> 00:28:48.400
It is coming to that point. All these shocks of AIDS

00:28:48.480 --> 00:28:53.200
and shocks of this drug, and all other problems,

00:28:53.280 --> 00:28:56.120
ecological problems, all these are facing us today,

00:28:57.800 --> 00:29:02.240
are bringing us to a point to see there’s something wrong somewhere.

00:29:04.360 --> 00:29:07.800
Many people are going back to organised religions,

00:29:07.880 --> 00:29:12.120
those who are not involved in the New Age.

00:29:13.440 --> 00:29:20.720
I hear in your talks you speak of Jesus. You speak of Mohammed.

00:29:20.840 --> 00:29:28.120
You speak of Buddha and Krishna. What is the essence of these teachings,

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:33.560
that you feel, brings all of these different prophets and holy people

00:29:33.640 --> 00:29:35.120
and incarnations together?

00:29:35.200 --> 00:29:41.080
The essence of their teaching was, all of them said one thing,

00:29:41.160 --> 00:29:46.160
depending on the time that they came, they might have given additional colour,

00:29:46.240 --> 00:29:52.920
additional forms. But the essence was that,

00:29:53.040 --> 00:29:58.600
“Seek the eternal”. And transitory is to be used,

00:29:58.680 --> 00:30:03.760
knowing that it is transitory, into its own limitations.

00:30:06.080 --> 00:30:15.600
And the religions that are formed today, are artificial religions.

00:30:15.680 --> 00:30:22.360
They are not innate religions, which are based on these great prophets

00:30:22.440 --> 00:30:31.240
and great incarnations. Because on a tree,

00:30:31.320 --> 00:30:34.164
there are lots of flowers.

00:30:34.244 --> 00:30:39.667
At different times they come, bloom, give their fragrance.

00:30:39.747 --> 00:30:45.174
These people have plucked these flowers,

00:30:45.963 --> 00:30:50.452
and which are dead. And they say,
“This is mine, this is mine, this is mine”.

00:30:51.440 --> 00:30:57.008
That’s why it looks so funny. They grew on the same sap of

00:30:57.089 --> 00:31:04.569
“Seek the eternal”, with genuineness. Most of them are money oriented.

00:31:04.960 --> 00:31:10.280
It’s all a big business. You cannot have business of Christ.

00:31:11.440 --> 00:31:15.800
You know how He took a hunter and hid people who were doing business.

00:31:15.880 --> 00:31:19.068
And now what will He do if He comes?

00:31:19.440 --> 00:31:25.680
Is there any religion that we practice that’s close to the type of idea

00:31:25.760 --> 00:31:28.320
or ideal that you have?

00:31:28.440 --> 00:31:33.200
So far, I haven’t seen any. I haven’t seen anyone.

00:31:33.280 --> 00:31:36.440
That’s why the fundamentalists who are going to religion

00:31:36.520 --> 00:31:42.080
will become Hitlers. Because they are not with reality.

00:31:45.320 --> 00:31:51.760
Now we have a religion which we call as the universal pure religion

00:31:51.840 --> 00:31:53.920
within ourselves, and that is to be awakened.

00:31:55.480 --> 00:31:58.440
And this happens with the process that you’ve discussed.

00:31:58.520 --> 00:32:03.160
Yes, when the Kundalini arises and pierces through six centres,

00:32:03.240 --> 00:32:07.480
and you get the connection with the Divine Power,

00:32:07.560 --> 00:32:13.200
and you establish the connection, then you are that pure religion.

00:32:13.280 --> 00:32:18.606
You are not to be told, “Don’t do this, don’t do that”. You just don’t do it.

00:32:18.920 --> 00:32:24.080
You’ve talked about it. But I don’t know if I’ve asked you,

00:32:24.160 --> 00:32:29.360
how does this happen? I mean, you said it’s spontaneous,

00:32:29.440 --> 00:32:35.463
but is it something that one needs to go in their room and ask for it?

00:32:36.040 --> 00:32:39.480
Nothing of the kind. If you just come to my program,

00:32:39.560 --> 00:32:42.840
I’ll work it out. And then you can work it out.

00:32:42.920 --> 00:32:44.273
It’s very simple.

00:32:44.353 --> 00:32:49.399
It’s like one enlightened light can enlighten another light.

00:32:49.479 --> 00:32:53.938
One candle which is not yet enlightened cannot do it.

00:32:54.018 --> 00:32:58.734
But another one does it. But there’s nothing special about it.

00:32:58.815 --> 00:33:01.500
You see, how do you do it? Just like that.

00:33:01.580 --> 00:33:05.313
Because it’s already there, it just works.

00:33:06.040 --> 00:33:12.880
Before we close, I wanted to ask whether the vision that you’ve portrayed,

00:33:12.960 --> 00:33:19.600
which is extremely beautiful, do you really think the world

00:33:19.680 --> 00:33:23.480
will achieve this peace and transformation?

00:33:23.560 --> 00:33:27.160
Oh, I’m very sure, very sure in my lifetime.

00:33:27.280 --> 00:33:31.986
I’m very sure now, in my lifetime, it will work out.

00:33:32.440 --> 00:33:35.712
I want to thank you very much for coming, Shri Mataji.

00:33:35.793 --> 00:33:39.233
May God bless you. Thank you very much. May God bless you. Thank you.